sequenceDiagram
    participant S as sensor
    participant M as mosquitto
    participant G as flood-gateway
    participant DB as influxdb
    participant TB as ThingsBoard

    S->>M: basin/{st}/sensor/telemetry (JSON, mỗi 2 s)
    M->>G: telemetry
    G->>G: validate + chuẩn hóa + tính tốc độ dâng
    G->>M: basin/{st}/gateway/normalized
    G->>DB: ghi water_telemetry
    G->>TB: v1/gateway/telemetry
    G->>G: rule engine → events + trạng thái mong muốn
